Subject: [PATCH] Add empty iproute2 patch series file

The iproute2 Makefile expects a patch/series file for stg import.
Create an empty one since no custom patches are needed.

Signed-off-by: apannerselva <apannerselva@marvell.com>
---
 src/iproute2/patch/series | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)
 create mode 100644 src/iproute2/patch/series

diff --git a/src/iproute2/patch/series b/src/iproute2/patch/series
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..8b13789
--- /dev/null
+++ b/src/iproute2/patch/series
@@ -0,0 +1 @@
+
